# Docs ‚Äî division of truth (canonical)

**Single source for doc boundaries.** Other rules/skills link here; do not duplicate the tables below.

Index: [`Docs/README.md`](../../Docs/README.md). Workflow: [`vibe-coding-workflow` SKILL](../skills/vibe-coding-workflow/SKILL.md).

**Editing `Docs/Archived/plans/`** ‚Äî history only; sync checklist **N/A** unless fixing broken links.

---

## Primary home

| Document | Owns | Must NOT own |
|----------|------|--------------|
| **`Active-Plan.md`** | **All open `[ ]`** ‚Äî active sprint (S3), P4, gates, queue, hardening index | Diagrams, policy prose, S4‚ÄìS8 staged tasks, changelogs |
| **`Wishlist.md`** | **S4‚ÄìS8 + Parallel + Backlog** staged `[ ]` only | Active sprint tasks, gates table, queue |
| **`Archived-Plan.md`** | Completed `[x]` lines; ¬ß S1 implementation notes | Open tasks |
| **`EngineArchitecture.md`** | Diagrams, **locked policies**, risks, non-goals | `[ ]` tasks, sprint logs |
| **`README.md`** | Index + **Active now** (WIP pointer) | Task lists, gates, duplicate file maps |
| **`{name}_Plan.md` (roadmap)** | Design / steps for one topic | Queue duplicates |
| **`{name}_Plan.md` + `_Progress` (WIP)** | One in-flight task | Second WIP pair at `Docs/` root |
| **Epic plans** (`hybrid-deferred`, `ddgi`) | Stage 2‚Äì3 breakdown | Executable `[ ]` queue |
| **`SprintPlan.md`** | One-line redirect to README | Content duplicated elsewhere |

