## What to edit (minimize touch)

| Event | Edit | Do **not** edit |
|-------|------|-----------------|
| Open / close task | `Active-Plan.md` | Wishlist, README (unless WIP) |
| Task done | Move line ‚Üí `Archived-Plan.md`; remove from Active-Plan | Wishlist, epic plans, Architecture |
| Promote Wishlist ‚Üí active | Add `[ ]` to Active-Plan; Wishlist ‚Üí index pointer only | Gates in Wishlist, duplicate task lists |
| Vibe kickoff | `README.md` **Active now** + `{Plan}_Progress.md` | Active-Plan queue unless scope changed |
| Vibe close | Progress closeout ‚Üí `Archived/plans/`; clear README **Active now** | EngineArchitecture unless policy |
| **Locked policy** (tree below) | `EngineArchitecture.md` + code/shaders | Wishlist |
| Deferred milestone | `Wishlist.md` only | Active-Plan |
| Gate met | `Active-Plan.md` gates row (‚úì) | Wishlist gates table *(removed ‚Äî use Active-Plan)* |

