## Locked policy? (decision tree)

1. Layer boundary moved? ‚Üí **yes, policy**
2. Descriptor model changed? ‚Üí **yes, policy**
3. Extract / record contract changed? ‚Üí **yes, policy**
4. Transparent / Stage 2 depth rule changed? ‚Üí **yes, policy**
5. Struct fields / bindings only ‚Üí code + MSBuild; Architecture if (2) narrative shifts
6. Task done, no 1‚Äì4 ‚Üí Active-Plan ‚Üí Archived-Plan only

---

## Agent `@`

| Goal | `@` |
|------|-----|
| Next task | `Active-Plan.md` |
| Layer / policy | `EngineArchitecture.md` |
| WIP steps | `{Task}_Plan.md` + `_Progress.md` |
| Staged S4+ | `Wishlist.md` |
| History | `Archived-Plan.md` / `Archived/plans/` |

