## Anti-patterns

- Gates / queue / open `[ ]` in Wishlist or README
- Same table in Active-Plan and Architecture
- `[x]` in Active-Plan or Wishlist
- Architecture edit on every task close
- Second WIP Plan+Progress pair at Docs root
